<br>
But, if your powerleveling requires that you log on and begin to killsteal from a group because they are camping the spawn you want is that cool? I would tend to think not but maybe you believe this is fine, perhaps you also feel this is wrong. <br>
<br>
Now lets look at a guild of people in around the level 50 range that are buffing to fight Lozidal for the very first time in what will be a very tough fight for them. Suddenly 2 groups of level 60's run up to turtle and proceed to demolish it as they have no need to spend preparations on what is now an easy spawn for them. Is this right and cool?<br>
<br>
