dy petition! You eat that exp loss and you like it cause now you are playing with no preformed thoughts of right or wrong, people play the way they want and if you dont like it tough. You just lost your level because of the train? boo fucking hoo, at least it made a 1337 screenshot for me seeing all you guys getting stepped on. Most fun I ever had in EQ, just the way I like to play. You want no rules there ya go then, lets play. <p>Tropics Delight Shadowknight of the Greenmist</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/usiggymk5.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SiggyMk5</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Contributing Member</span><br>  Posts: 245<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/5/01 5:51:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=329.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www-scf.usc.edu/~rabiega/sigs/icon.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: paradox</span><hr size=1> The leezard will return....<br>
